WEBVTT

17:15.310 --> 17:16.629 line:80%
settle those accounts,

17:16.629 --> 17:18.159 line:80%
and I'll return the letter.

17:18.350 --> 17:21.149 line:80%
You can't blame us
for calling off the engagement.

17:21.200 --> 17:23.730 line:80%
That fortune teller said
your fate is cursed!

17:23.909 --> 17:25.310 line:80%
I can't let my Yan marry a woman like you
